WEBVTT

00:00.254 --> 00:02.309
Hi! This is your host, Naomi.

00:02.619 --> 00:06.408
I'd like to show you the top 5 travel destinations of India.

00:06.911 --> 00:08.509
Number 5: Delhi.

00:08.770 --> 00:10.575
Start with the country's capital.

00:10.771 --> 00:14.045
Soak in the exciting energy of this fast-growing city...

00:14.143 --> 00:17.567
...while enjoying the landmarks that tell the story of Delhi's past.

00:17.797 --> 00:19.571
Number 4: Kerala.

00:19.703 --> 00:21.633
Locals call it "God's country."

00:21.933 --> 00:22.968
And why not?

00:23.204 --> 00:25.573
This is where you'll find great beaches...

00:25.657 --> 00:29.874
...and, of course, the calm and meditative, world-famous backwaters.

00:29.968 --> 00:31.615
Number 3: Mumbai,...

00:31.758 --> 00:34.176
...the most cosmopolitan city of India.

00:34.337 --> 00:37.143
Besides its plethora of restaurants and nightlife,...

00:37.356 --> 00:40.727
...the city has a remarkable diversity of beautiful architecture.

00:40.837 --> 00:42.763
Number 2: Rajasthan,...

00:43.125 --> 00:44.991
...the state of princes and palaces.

00:45.137 --> 00:46.991
Set amidst a desert landscape,...

00:47.101 --> 00:50.966
...this otherworldly destination showcases India's rich heritage...

00:51.046 --> 00:52.480
...like no other place.

00:52.654 --> 00:54.371
Number 1: Agra.

00:54.492 --> 00:57.185
This is the city where you'll find Taj Mahal,...

00:57.347 --> 00:58.913
...one of the Wonders of the World,...

00:59.014 --> 01:00.811
...an awe-inspiring symbol of love...

01:00.903 --> 01:03.725
...and a widowed king's promise to his beloved queen.

01:04.072 --> 01:06.431
Keep watching our travel video series.

01:06.563 --> 01:07.601
See you next time!

